  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Imagine that every time you fall asleep, a new adventure awaits you...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Episode 2 is the sequel to the popular Adventurer game, where the main protagonist dives into a new adventure whenever he goes to sleep. Will he be able to wake up, or will he remain trapped in the dream? It’s up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D maps and battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of camera angles and perspectives</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Episodic story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Humor</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controls:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movement: Arrow keys</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rotate: Q, E</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zoom in/out: C, V</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Camera angle: R, F</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Change camera: B</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inventory: X</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action/Use: ENTER</p></li></ul>",
